[HR][/HR]

[SIZE=5][B]Installation[/B][/SIZE]

[SIZE=4][B]Paper[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST=1]
[*]Drop [ICODE]PvPIndexBattles-<version>.jar[/ICODE] into your server's [ICODE]plugins/[/ICODE] folder.
[*]Start the server — config files are generated automatically.
[*]Stop the server and set your API key in [ICODE]plugins/PvPIndexBattles/config.yml[/ICODE]:
[CODE=yaml]api:
  api_key: "your-api-key-here"

server:
  id: "my-server"[/CODE]
[*]Restart and run [ICODE]/pvpindex[/ICODE] to confirm the plugin loaded correctly.
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B]Velocity (optional)[/B][/SIZE]

Drop [ICODE]PvPIndexBattles-velocity-<version>.jar[/ICODE] into your Velocity [ICODE]plugins/[/ICODE] folder and configure [ICODE]plugins/pvpindex-battles/config.properties[/ICODE] with the same API key and shared secret used on your Paper backends.

[HR][/HR]

[SIZE=5][B]Commands[/B][/SIZE]

[SIZE=4][B]/battle — Player commands[/B][/SIZE]

[TABLE]
[TR]
[TH]Command[/TH]
[TH]Description[/TH]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/battle[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Open the matchmaking mode selection GUI[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/battle challenge <player> [mode][/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Challenge another player to a duel[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/battle accept <id>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Accept an incoming challenge[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/battle decline <id>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Decline an incoming challenge[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/battle leave[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Leave the queue or forfeit an active battle[/TD]
[/TR]
[/TABLE]

[SIZE=4][B]/pvpindex — Admin commands[/B][/SIZE]

[TABLE]
[TR]
[TH]Command[/TH]
[TH]Permission[/TH]
[TH]Description[/TH]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpindex reload[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.reload[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Reload plugin configuration[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpindex submissions[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.admin[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]List pending battle submissions[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpindex sync[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.admin[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Retry unsubmitted battles[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpindex retryfailed[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.admin[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Retry failed API submissions[/TD]
[/TR]
[/TABLE]

[SIZE=4][B]/pvpmod — Moderation commands[/B][/SIZE]

[TABLE]
[TR]
[TH]Command[/TH]
[TH]Permission[/TH]
[TH]Description[/TH]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpmod watch <player>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.mod[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Spectate a live battle[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpmod replay <id>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.mod[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Play back a recorded battle[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpmod report <player> <reason>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.mod.report[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Report a player[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpmod ban <player> <duration> <reason>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.mod.ban[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Ban a player from PvPIndex battles[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/pvpmod unban <player>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD][ICODE]pvpindex.mod.ban[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Unban a player[/TD]
[/TR]
[/TABLE]

